  "description": "<p>近几年智能穿戴设备非常火爆，不过针对残疾人士使用还真不多。而盲人现在依然需要拐杖或者导盲犬来领路，<strong>这是相当不方便的，而今天这款智能鞋Le Chal，就能让盲人独立行走。这款智能鞋，由设计师Anirudh Sharma设计，智能鞋名为Le Chal，印度中为“带我到那里”。设计这款智能鞋的主要目的是带领盲人到其指定的位置，同时避免可能发生的碰撞以及障碍物躲避等。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2f1439e1/sc/9/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245838.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%9E%8B+%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245838.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%9E%8B+%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245838.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%9E%8B+%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245838.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%9E%8B+%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245838.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%9E%8B+%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0\" target=\"